1977;;Bobby Deerfield;;American;;Sydney Pollack;;Al Pacino, Marthe Keller;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bobby_Deerfield;;Formula One auto racer Bobby Deerfield is a calculating, control-obsessed loner who has become used to winning the checkered flag on the track. But after he witnesses a fiery crash that kills a teammate and seriously wounds a competitor, Deerfield becomes unsettled by the spectre of death.<br><br>During a visit to the survivor, Deerfield's world is further set askew when he meets Lillian Morelli (Marthe Keller), a quirky, impulsive woman racing against time.